ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of ROSSANA BUONPENSIERE of Winnipeg, Manitoba, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Manitoba, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 1, 2014, in the place of Raymond Desrochers.
